				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I still like this idea alot but I think we could make it alot easier than having seperate new spells. Give current spells this effect. 
<br />
Mage pet burnout could have the shield. Make it so that each level of burnout -stun- has a chance to go off on a higher level mob and maybe at a greater percent chance. (stronger than ds version to help survivability)
<br />
Give our DS the stun. If our DS is barely stronger than a druids and doesn't last as long, give it this ability plus the damage.
<br />
Finally, add the stun to our XPG and Transon spell. Give it a higher rate to proc then others and give it a max number of times it can go off. Lets say XPG stuns 6 times then XPG drops. 
<br />

<br />
Biltil</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
